 destituito per malversazione (1946) ed espulso (1947)."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q4147094", "itemLabel": "Karl Hofmaier", "dhsid": "024671", "namefr": "", "articlefr": "", "namede": "", "articlede": "", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "118816241"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q4147094", "wikipedia_page_title": null, "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": null, "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/024671/2007-12-18"}